{"tid":1382732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想買能量棒同朱古力餅俾前線既學生哥","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:28:25.000Z","uid":283071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0677f5f6731b0300d9e661b8f018e3410e5f1421","tid":1382732,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"我呢兩日見到網上面有好多人話 <br />\n好多企前線既學生哥開始用盡零用錢 冇錢食飯<br />\n<br />\n可能肥絲打我個人鍾意食野<br />\n而且我個人認為 做咩都好 餓住個肚去做 好難會成功<br />\n同埋要你地餓住個肚去抗爭 <br />\n我於心不忍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飯劵 呢d我暫時唔想<br />\n因為唔想過錢落任何組織手上(如有錯 勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n我就想買d能量棒同朱古力餅<br />\n(外國有女人係冰天雪地下靠兩塊朱古力餅生存左6日)<br />\n所以朱古力餅係好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題係 我可以交去邊個手上？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n交去鄺俊宇辦事處係咪好方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d03f4a81d88718fadeb5bf4e7ea6ea1f06555a8","tid":1382732,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:12:52.000Z","msg":"戴住個口罩都唔方便食<br />\n又多鏡頭"},{"pid":"b31aeebd347c4ee6338cc05605b29a65490cf232","tid":1382732,"uid":199640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:14:24.000Z","msg":"跑開山/馬拉松既朋友應該都有食過energy gel，係最快最有效補充能量既食品<br />\n好多時候係運動鋪都會放d就快過期既energy gel/bar/chew...etc出來，賣得好平，講緊平到幾蚊包<br />\n可以同鋪頭講一次過買晒佢，個價錢係會好平好平，同埋據我所知好多運動用品鋪都係撐我方，有機會免費/極平都唔出奇<br />\n我list一d平時去開/去過既鋪頭，大家再提議下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/actionpandahk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Factionpandahk%2F&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=59e43bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/actionpandahk/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TrailSportPlus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTrailSportPlus%2F&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6